replyContent: Star Fragments are awarded at the end of a level, as drops from enemies, and as Nexus Global Rewards when all players' progress on a map hits a milestone. Beat Campaign levels on new difficulties to earn a Completion bonus to Star Fragments. If you're using the Full interface layout, you may prefer the compact option - switch in the game settings.

replyContent: If you use your device's "Home" button to exit out of the game, your progress within the level will automatically be saved. When you resume the game will either automatically pick off where you left off (if the game remained open but asleep in the background), or there will be a "Continue" option at the Main Menu.

replyContent: The top level Artillery tower gains a damage over time effect.
